---
layout: base.njk
pageKey: care
title: "Website care plans"
permalink: care.html
description: Keep your site fast, secure, updated, and converting — managed website care plans from $99/mo. Hosting, monitoring, updates, and ongoing improvements, handled by the people who built it.
---

{# ===== Hero =========================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight has-aurora">
  <div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container container--narrow center">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">Care plans</span>
    <h1 class="section__title">We keep it running — from $99/mo</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      A website isn’t “done” — it needs hosting, updates, monitoring, and the occasional change.
      A care plan hands all of that to the people who built it, so it stays fast, secure, and
      working while you run your business.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row btn-row--center mt-6">
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="#plans">See plans</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get a free scan</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== What's covered ================================================= #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">What’s covered</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Off your plate, on ours</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--auto">
      <article class="card" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="card__title">Fast &amp; online</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Managed hosting, SSL, and uptime monitoring so your site stays quick and reachable.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <h3 class="card__title">Secure &amp; current</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Updates and security monitoring so nothing goes stale or gets exploited.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <h3 class="card__title">Always editable</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Send us the change — new hours, a new photo, a new page — and we handle it.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <h3 class="card__title">Always improving</h3>
        <p class="card__text">On higher plans we keep tuning the site to win more leads, not just keep the lights on.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Plans ========================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight" id="plans">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">Plans</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Simple monthly care</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">Month-to-month, cancel anytime. Already a client? We’ll roll your site straight in.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--3">
      {% for plan in site.carePlans %}
        <article
          id="{{ plan.key }}"
          class="price{% if plan.featured %} price--popular{% endif %}"
          data-reveal
          data-reveal-delay="{{ loop.index0 }}"
        >
          {% if plan.featured %}<span class="price__flag">Most popular</span>{% endif %}
          <h2 class="price__name">{{ plan.name }}</h2>
          <p class="price__amount">{{ plan.price }} <small>{{ plan.cadence }}</small></p>
          <p class="price__desc">{{ plan.blurb }}</p>
          <ul class="price__features">
            {% for feature in plan.features %}
              <li>{{ feature }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          <div class="price__cta">
            <a
              class="btn {% if plan.featured %}btn--primary{% else %}btn--secondary{% endif %} btn--block"
              href="{{ plan.checkoutUrl if plan.checkoutUrl else site.cta.url }}"
              {% if plan.checkoutUrl %}rel="noopener"{% endif %}
            >
              {% if plan.checkoutUrl %}Start {{ plan.name }} — {{ plan.price }}{{ plan.cadence }}{% else %}Get started{% endif %}
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="note-card mt-7" data-reveal>
      <span class="note-card__tag">Not a client yet?</span>
      <p>
        We can take over an existing site or build you a new one first. <a href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Start with a free scan</a> and we’ll tell you which plan fits — or whether you need one at all.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Closing CTA =================================================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="cta-band__title">Stop worrying about your website</h2>
      <p class="cta-band__text">
        Hand it to the people who built it. We’ll keep it fast, secure, and converting — you get
        back to running the business.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row btn-row--center">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" href="pricing.html">See pricing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
